sequenceDiagram
    actor Browser
    participant API as Spring Boot
    participant Redis
    participant Qdrant
    participant Cohere
    participant Claude as Claude Haiku

    Browser->>API: POST /api/chat/stream

    API->>API: Rate limit check (5/min · 20/day per IP)

    API->>API: Classify question (rule-based, zero LLM cost)
    alt INVALID / OUT_OF_SCOPE / STRATEGIC / CONTACT
        API-->>Browser: SSE early-return message + done
    end

    API->>Redis: GET session turn count
    alt Turn limit reached (30 turns)
        API-->>Browser: SSE limit message + done
    end

    API->>Redis: GET conversation history (last 2 turns)
    API->>API: Extract company focus from question + history
    API->>API: Resolve ambiguous pronouns using last answer snippet

    API->>Qdrant: Hybrid search — dense + BM25 sparse, RRF fusion
    Note over API,Qdrant: candidateK = 10, company-scoped filter
    Qdrant-->>API: Top 10 candidates (RRF ranked)

    API->>Cohere: Rerank (rerank-v3.5)
    Cohere-->>API: Top 5 by cross-encoder score (min 0.18)

    API->>API: Company scope post-filter

    API-->>Browser: SSE event:sources (chunk previews)

    API->>API: Assemble prompt (system + typeHint + history + context + question)
    API->>Claude: Streaming generate (claude-haiku, maxTokens=800)

    loop Per token
        Claude-->>API: token
        API-->>Browser: SSE event:message
    end

    API->>Redis: Append Q&A to conversation history
    API-->>Browser: SSE event:done
